# shadcn-vue Component Installation

## Always install with the pinned version

```bash
npx shadcn-vue@2.7.4 add <component> --cwd ./frontend --yes
```

Never use `@latest` — it installs an incompatible version.

## Component library dependency

The project is migrating from `radix-vue` to `reka-ui`. New components should use `reka-ui`.
Existing radix-based components (Button, Label, Separator, Dialog, ScrollArea) will be
migrated in a future chore. Do not mix dependencies within a single component.
